OL,4,CBROADCAST STUDIOS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2013FThe BBC News channel broadcasts
OL,7,Ffrom BBC Television Centre for the
OL,8,Ffinal time.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe final programme - based in Studio
OL,11,FN6 - is presented by Simon McCoy and
OL,12,FSophie Long and went out 8.30am - 1pm.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG2013FThe BBC News at One (BBC One/BBC
OL,15,FNews channel) is the first domestic
OL,16,Fnews programme to be broadcast from New
OL,17,FBroadcasting House, London.
OL,18,
OL,19,FThe programme is broadcast from Studio
OL,20,FE and presented by Sophie Raworth.
